reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Easy to use and great price

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My son loves it!
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this around Christmas for my son. He had everything scattered everywhere and half the time, kept misplacing his airpods. This is the only one so far you don’t have to take the phone case off in order to charge which is a plus! Now he has a habit of putting everything to charge before bed. This is such an awesome price and good quality. Highly recommend:)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I use this product for charging my phone when I travel for work. I recently upgraded to an iPhone 15 that charges with USB-C or Mag safe. I also have a separate work phone that still charges using Lightning. My EarPods are also old school Lightning chargeable. This charger accommodates all my devices at once, and easily fits in my suitcase for travel!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Just a lot of unnecessary USB plugs
reviews.reviewText: This unit has a lot of USB plugs no one ever uses anymore, no fast charging and no manual on how to hook up the watch as it doesn’t have a watch charger built in. Just too much to figure out and it is way too big for what it needs to be as I only need to charge 1 phone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars All device charger
reviews.reviewText: This charger is great! we live in a family of 5 and there was rarely any charging space for everyone. I like that this charger is versatile, aka not just for apple products. Made our counter more organized as well!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Not only a good price but the charge stand is perfect for our 16 yo son we bought an Apple Watch and air pods for Christmas now instead of keeping up with all of the cords it’s all in one and perfect for him! He loves it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It’s nice to be able to charge multiple devices at once. The watch charger doesn’t come with it but for the price you figure it wouldn’t anyways. So far I’ve been able to charge two phones my watch and AirPods at once. One phone on the wireless pad and the other on the rotating charger. It’s a good bang for your buck.
